We will curate a diverse set of datasets specifically designed to test the performance of Sequential Recommender Systems (SRSs). The criteria for inclusion will be datasets with well-defined sequential patterns, from diverse domains such as e-commerce, banking, and social media, and with varying levels of sparsity. The criteria for exclusion will be datasets with insufficient sequential information or known biases and anomalies.

#### Evaluation Protocols
To enhance existing evaluation protocols, we will incorporate cross-validation techniques, use synthetic datasets to test robustness, and compare with existing evaluation protocols to highlight improvements.

